|-.
|[[Battle of Baghdad (2003)|Battle of Baghdad]]||{{dts|format=dmy|2003|04|03}}||{{dts|format=dmy|2003|04|12}}||Baghdad||Battle: The invasion of the city commenced three days after Allied forces had secured the Baghdad airport |}
